<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:og="http://ogp.me/ns#" xmlns:fb="http://www.facebook.com/2008/fbml">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="keywords" content="Task,Management,Twitter,Facebook,タスク管理,タスク共有">
<meta property="fb:admins" content="272550092773416">
<meta property="og:title" content="7kai Tasks">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://tasks.7kai.org/">
<meta property="og:image" content="https://tasks.7kai.org/static/img/logo-128.png">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="7kai Tasks">
<meta property="og:description" content="High Speed Social Task Management Service">
<title>7kai Tasks</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/bootstrap.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/signin.css" media="all">
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/jquery-ui-1.8.13.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/bootstrap-transition.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/bootstrap-carousel.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/app-core.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/app-base.js"></script>
<script src="/static/js/app-base-signin.js"></script>
</head>
<body id="index-page">
<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="brand">7kai Tasks</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
      </div>
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h1
          data-setup="localize"
          data-text-ja="最速をあなたに！"
        >Fastest For You.</h1>
        <p>
          <span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="シンプルで軽快なインターフェースとソーシャルコラボレーション。"
          >Simple and lightness Interface, and Social Collaboration.</span><br>
          <span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="煩雑なタスク管理から解放され、重要な事に集中しましょう。"
          >You can concentrate on an important thing.</span></p>
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel">
          <!-- Carousel items -->
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="item active">
              <img src="/static/img/tasks-home.png">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="/static/img/tasks-gantt.png">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="/static/img/tasks-changes.png">
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Carousel nav -->
          <a class="carousel-control left" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">&lsaquo;</a>
          <a class="carousel-control right" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a>
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="/signin/twitter/signin">
          <div><button class="btn btn-large btn-primary">Connect with Twitter</button></div>
        </form>
        <form method="post" action="/signin/facebook/signin">
          <div><button class="btn btn-large btn-primary">Connect with Facebook</button></div>
        </form>
        <div class="alert alert-info">
          By signing up, you accept 7kai Tasks's <a href="/static/tos.html">terms</a> of use and <a href="/static/privacy.html">privacy policy</a>.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Social</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-social.png">
            <p
              data-setup="localize"
              data-text-ja="ソーシャルからフレンドを加えられます。"
            >Easily added a friend from social account.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Multi list with tag</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-tag.png">
            <p
              data-setup="localize"
              data-text-ja="4つの色でリストを分類できます。"
            >You can assort it with a four colors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Quick Filter</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-filter.png">
            <p
              data-setup="localize"
              data-text-ja="関心にすぐアクセス出来ます。"
            >You can access interest immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Flexible</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-flexible.png">
            <p
              data-setup="localize"
              data-text-ja="多くの状態・フラグを扱えます。"
            >Support many status and flagged.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Open</li>
              <li>Start</li>
              <li>Fixed</li>
              <li>Closed</li>
              <li>Pending</li>
              <li>Star</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Public</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-format.png">
            <p
              data-setup="localize"
              data-text-ja="多くの公開フォーマットに対応しています。"
            >Support many public format.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>RSS</li>
              <li>iCal</li>
              <li>JSON</li>
              <li>JSONP</li>
              <li>HTML</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Chrome Extensions</h3>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-ext.png">
            <p>Official Chrome Extensions <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/dolhpjcchfcnkcanamhgcgbnmcogdank">here</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="チュートリアル"
      >Quick Tutorial</h2>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-new-task.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="基本操作"
          >Basic Operation</span> ... [N] [Enter] [ESC] [C] [Shift-C]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[N]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="タスク登録ウィンドウを表示"
              >Open New Task Window.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>Input and [Enter]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="タスクを登録"
              >New Task.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[ESC]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="タスク登録ウィンドウを閉じる"
              >Close New Task Window.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Enter]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="選択されているタスクを完了"
              >Closed the Task.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[C]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="完了タスクを表示"
              >Show Closed Task.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-C]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="完了タスクをクリア"
              >Clear Closed Task.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ドラッグアンドドロップ"
      >Drag and Drop</h2>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-dd.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="ドロップ先"
          >Drop to</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="リスト名"
              >over the List</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="リストへ移動"
              >move to the list.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="タスク"
              >over the Task</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="タスク配下に移動"
              >belong to the task.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="画面内余白"
              >Out</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="サブタスク解除（サブタスク限定）"
              >move to the root.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ショートカットキー"
      >More Shortcut Keys</h2>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-help.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="ヘルプ"
          >Help</span> ... [?] or [/]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[?] or [/]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="ショートカットキー表示"
              >Show Shortcut Keys.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-menu.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="メニュー切り替え"
          >Main Menu Switch</span> ... [Shift-Left/H] [Shift-Right/L]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-Right] or [Shift-L]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="次のメニュー"
              >Next Menu.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-Left] or [Shift-H]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="前のメニュー"
              >Previous Menu.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-selection.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="タスク選択"
          >Task Selection</span> ... [Up] [Down] or [J] [K]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[Down] or [J]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="次のタスク"
              >Next Task</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Up] or [K]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="前のタスク"
              >Previous Task</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-Down] or [Shift-J]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="次のリスト"
              >Next List</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-Up] or [Shift-K]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="前のリスト"
              >Previous List</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-tour-operation.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="タスク操作"
          >Task Operation</span> ... [Enter] [Space] [P] [*] [E] [Shift-N]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[Enter]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="完了"
              >Closed.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Space]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="進捗更新"
              >Rotate Progress.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[P]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="保留 (on/off)"
              >Pending. ( on/off )</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[*]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="スター (on/off)"
              >Starred. ( on/off )</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[E]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="編集"
              >Edit.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[Shift-N]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="新しいサブタスク"
              >New Sub Task.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="thumbnails">
        <li class="span4">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-filter.png" alt="">
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="span6">
          <h3><span
            data-setup="localize"
            data-text-ja="クイックフィルター"
          >Quick Filter</span> ... [T] [V] [R] [S] [C]</h3>
          <table class="table table-striped">
            <tr>
              <th>[T]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="今日迄"
              >Todo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[V]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="確認待ち"
              >Verify</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[R]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="依頼中"
              >Request</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[S]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="スター"
              >Star</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>[C]</th>
              <td
                data-setup="localize"
                data-text-ja="完了済"
              >Close</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
